  <section id="overview">
    <h2>OLSP Community Builders Overview &amp; Pricing</h2>
    <p>The OLSP System runs several membership tiers. Community Builders occupies the mid-range: above the free account and the $7 Megalink one-time purchase, above the Live Profit Builders monthly subscription, and below the Team Builders and VIP tiers. Vendor and affiliate materials frame this level as the point where members transition from solo affiliates into team-builders — earning not just from their own promotions but from the activity of affiliates they refer into the system.</p>

    <h3>What's Included (Vendor and Affiliate Claims)</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Mega Builder marketing suite:</strong> white-label GoHighLevel account with funnel and page builder (TD Pages), CRM and pipeline tracking, email autoresponder with pre-loaded OLSP sequences, calendar booking, and deep OLSP tracking integration.</li>
      <li><strong>Enhanced commission rates:</strong> 200% front-end commissions on own Megalink sales and second-tier earnings from referred members' activity.</li>
      <li><strong>Private community-building tools:</strong> ability to create invite-only OLSP communities with unique links that sign referred members directly under you.</li>
      <li><strong>Public hub sites via TD Pages:</strong> branded resource hubs that act as a link-in-bio page for your offers and content.</li>
      <li><strong>TOFFEE method training:</strong> multi-hour Facebook audience building, posting frameworks, DM handling, and Zoom sales course.</li>
      <li><strong>Weekly live guru huddles:</strong> reportedly five sessions per week from different topic-specialist trainers.</li>
      <li><strong>Group coaching by topic:</strong> dedicated sessions covering solo ads, YouTube ads, email marketing, and other traffic channels.</li>
      <li><strong>Traffic rotator access:</strong> shared pool of solo-ad traffic purchased by OLSP leadership and distributed across participating members.</li>
      <li><strong>Viral Hub credits:</strong> approximately 1,000 credits per month for incentivized engagement campaigns within the OLSP community.</li>
      <li><strong>Expanded affiliate product library:</strong> access to more OLSP tools, solo ads, and automation products to promote, with reported commissions of 40–60% on mid-range products.</li>
    </ul>

    <Callout type="warn">
      <strong>Claims caution:</strong> The feature list above reflects vendor and affiliate descriptions, not independently verified inclusions. We could not test the software, confirm the live session schedule, or audit the traffic rotator. Verify current inclusions directly with OLSP before purchasing.
    </Callout>

